premise_source_doc_sentence: Fish head casserole  (  Chinese : 砂锅鱼头 shā guō yú tóu  )  is a seafood dish from China .
Lobster Newberg  (  also spelled Lobster Newburg  )  is an American seafood dish made from lobster , butter , cream , cognac , sherry , eggs , and Cayenne pepper .
Ceviche  (  -LSB- seˈβitʃe -RSB-  )  is a seafood dish popular in the coastal regions of Latin America and the Caribbean .
